  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Weight loss is a frequent problem associated with Alzheimers disease (AD). Mirtazapine has
      weight loss as a frequent side effect.

      The aim of this retrospective study is to check whether mirtazapine 30 mg (once daily) can
      counteract weight loss in patients with AD or mixed dementia (AD + vascular).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
